name: Vintage Rose Gift Tags (x5)
description:
Pack of 5 'Vintage Rose' Gift tags, measuring 5cms x 3cms. 
Left blank on the reverse for your own message. 
Small tags made from pink rose printed card, topped with gold script vellum and a pink mulberry rose. Each tag has been strung with sage satin ribbon.

name: Carte Postal Gift Tags (x3)
description:
"Oh la la" 

Pack of 3 'Carte Postal' Gift tags, measuring 10.5cms x 5.5cms. 
Left blank on the reverse for your own message. 
Aged manilla shipping tags with hand stamped design. Tags have each been strung with twine.

name: With Love Gift Tags (x3)
description:
Pack of 3 Gift tags, measuring 12.5cms x 6,5cms. 
Left blank on the reverse for your own message. 
Aged manilla shipping tags with khaki floral design paper, a selection of buttons and east of India "with Love" ribbon. Tags have each been strung with sage & cream satin ribbons.

name: Alice in Wonderland Card set (x5)
description:
Pack of 5 white Alice in Wonderland hand stamped greeting cards, left blank for your own message. 
Each card measures 11 x 8cms 

Each pack of cards has one of each of the following images: 
-Mad Hatter 
-Alice & the Cheshire Cat 
-White Rabbit 
-Alice "drink me" 
-Hookah-Smoking Caterpillar 

the envelopes in this pack have a mushroom stamped in the bottom left corner and the whole pack comes wrapped in claret satin ribbon with an "EAT ME" swing tag.

name: Lady Bird Gift Tags (x5)
description:
Pack of 5 'Lady Bird' Gift tags, measuring 5cms x 3cms. 
Left blank on the reverse for your own message. 
Small tags made from scrapbooking paper, reinforced with plain green card. Each tag has a little wooden hand painted lady bird and has been strung with red satin ribbon.
